file.name: spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Go Lessons Spec
  description: Go Lessons Spec
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https'
paths:
  "/participant":
    post:
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Created
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Participant"


components:
  schemas:
    Participant:
      type: object
      properties:
        track:
          type: string
          enum:
            - Advanced
            - Beginners
        email:
          type: string
          format: email
